{
  "video_id": "9B5Z-7ELMO8",
  "title": "A practical way to help the homeless find work and safety | Richard J. Berry",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12687.0,
      "end_time": 16358.0,
      "text": "So, raise your hand if you&#39;ve seen somebody in your city"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16383.0,
      "end_time": 19762.0,
      "text": "standing on a corner, holding a sign like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22229.0,
      "end_time": 23477.0,
      "text": "I think we all have."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23502.0,
      "end_time": 24666.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re being honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24691.0,
      "end_time": 27308.0,
      "text": "at least one time, have you wondered if they mean it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28578.0,
      "end_time": 31485.0,
      "text": "If we offered them a job, would they really take it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31509.0,
      "end_time": 33990.0,
      "text": "And what would that job mean to them in their lives?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35630.0,
      "end_time": 37864.0,
      "text": "Well, this is a story about what happened in my city"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37888.0,
      "end_time": 39440.0,
      "text": "when we decided to find out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40532.0,
      "end_time": 43919.0,
      "text": "when we decided to think differently about panhandling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43943.0,
      "end_time": 46839.0,
      "text": "and lift people up through the dignity of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47954.0,
      "end_time": 49731.0,
      "text": "We call it, \"There&#39;s a Better Way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50204.0,
      "end_time": 51697.0,
      "text": "We call it There&#39;s a Better Way"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51721.0,
      "end_time": 54758.0,
      "text": "because I believe there&#39;s a better way to get the money you need"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54783.0,
      "end_time": 56450.0,
      "text": "than panhandling on the corner."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57800.0,
      "end_time": 60978.0,
      "text": "I believe there&#39;s a better way to help your brothers and sisters in need"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61200.0,
      "end_time": 63335.0,
      "text": "than handing a few dollars out the car window."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64294.0,
      "end_time": 66192.0,
      "text": "We know there&#39;s dignity in work."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66930.0,
      "end_time": 70326.0,
      "text": "We also know that people are much more likely to invest in themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70350.0,
      "end_time": 73990.0,
      "text": "if they believe that their community is willing to invest in them first."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75304.0,
      "end_time": 78607.0,
      "text": "And because we&#39;re all wired to be kind and compassionate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78631.0,
      "end_time": 82136.0,
      "text": "it always feels good to hand a couple of dollars to someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82160.0,
      "end_time": 83360.0,
      "text": "that is in need."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84627.0,
      "end_time": 88540.0,
      "text": "But if you talk to panhandlers, many of them will tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88780.0,
      "end_time": 93268.0,
      "text": "that your few dollars don&#39;t necessarily go towards feeding the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93292.0,
      "end_time": 95298.0,
      "text": "they go towards feeding an addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96304.0,
      "end_time": 97593.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a better way."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98409.0,
      "end_time": 99681.0,
      "text": "My name is Richard Berry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99705.0,
      "end_time": 102720.0,
      "text": "and I have one of the best jobs in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102960.0,
      "end_time": 104530.0,
      "text": "I get to be the mayor of a great American city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104554.0,
      "end_time": 106122.0,
      "text": "Albuquerque, New Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107766.0,
      "end_time": 113211.0,
      "text": "I was at lunch on July 17, 2015, in my great American city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113993.0,
      "end_time": 116217.0,
      "text": "and on my way back to city hall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 116241.0,
      "end_time": 118432.0,
      "text": "I saw this gentleman standing on a corner."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118896.0,
      "end_time": 120852.0,
      "text": "As you can see, he&#39;s holding a sign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120876.0,
      "end_time": 122791.0,
      "text": "and his sign says he wants a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123493.0,
      "end_time": 125335.0,
      "text": "But if you look closer at the picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125359.0,
      "end_time": 127598.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll see he&#39;s standing underneath a blue sign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127622.0,
      "end_time": 131734.0,
      "text": "and that sign says, if you need help, if you need food or shelter"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131758.0,
      "end_time": 133150.0,
      "text": "or you&#39;d like to donate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133390.0,
      "end_time": 135834.0,
      "text": "please call 311, our community service number."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137293.0,
      "end_time": 142174.0,
      "text": "So why is this guy standing underneath my sign with his sign?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142889.0,
      "end_time": 145454.0,
      "text": "Well, we wondered if anybody would call that 311 sign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145478.0,
      "end_time": 147340.0,
      "text": "and as it turns out, they did --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147580.0,
      "end_time": 148789.0,
      "text": "11,000 times people called."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148813.0,
      "end_time": 150876.0,
      "text": "I put those up in about 30 intersections."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150901.0,
      "end_time": 154275.0,
      "text": "And we did connect them with food and shelter and services."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154299.0,
      "end_time": 156361.0,
      "text": "But yet he&#39;s still standing under my sign"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156385.0,
      "end_time": 158267.0,
      "text": "with a sign that says he wants a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159908.0,
      "end_time": 161515.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s simple: he wants a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163135.0,
      "end_time": 165547.0,
      "text": "So I decided to do something rare in government."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166139.0,
      "end_time": 170422.0,
      "text": "I decided to make the solution simpler rather than more complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170446.0,
      "end_time": 172971.0,
      "text": "I went back to my office, I gathered my staff around"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172995.0,
      "end_time": 175606.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"We&#39;re going to take this man at his word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175630.0,
      "end_time": 176815.0,
      "text": "and others like him."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176839.0,
      "end_time": 179616.0,
      "text": "The man says he wants a job, we&#39;re going to give him a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179640.0,
      "end_time": 183448.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to make our city an even better place in the meantime.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183919.0,
      "end_time": 186128.0,
      "text": "You see, Albuquerque is a beautiful place."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 186152.0,
      "end_time": 187422.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re a mile high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187447.0,
      "end_time": 189553.0,
      "text": "the Sandia Mountains on the east,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189577.0,
      "end_time": 192117.0,
      "text": "the Rio Grande runs through the center of the city;"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192141.0,
      "end_time": 195204.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re the home of the Albuquerque International Balloon Fiesta."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 195229.0,
      "end_time": 196393.0,
      "text": "On a day like today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196417.0,
      "end_time": 199361.0,
      "text": "you could literally ski this morning and golf this afternoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199851.0,
      "end_time": 201742.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s always something to do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 201766.0,
      "end_time": 203868.0,
      "text": "always weeds to pull, litter to pick up."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204625.0,
      "end_time": 207561.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re going to have an initiative like this in your city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207585.0,
      "end_time": 209480.0,
      "text": "you have to ask yourself two questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209504.0,
      "end_time": 212173.0,
      "text": "First one is: Is there anything left to do in your city?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 212198.0,
      "end_time": 213380.0,
      "text": "And if the answer is no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213404.0,
      "end_time": 215811.0,
      "text": "would you please give me your mayor&#39;s phone number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215836.0,
      "end_time": 217159.0,
      "text": "because I need some advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217183.0,
      "end_time": 218190.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218214.0,
      "end_time": 220481.0,
      "text": "But the second question you have to ask is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220505.0,
      "end_time": 222869.0,
      "text": "Are your solutions to panhandling working?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224506.0,
      "end_time": 225792.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re like Albuquerque,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 225816.0,
      "end_time": 228462.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re taking the punitive approach like we used to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228486.0,
      "end_time": 231619.0,
      "text": "handing out tickets to panhandlers or those who give them money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231644.0,
      "end_time": 234318.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to suggest that your solutions aren&#39;t working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234342.0,
      "end_time": 237940.0,
      "text": "and I know you&#39;re not getting to the root of your problem in your city."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238605.0,
      "end_time": 240226.0,
      "text": "So if you have something to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241500.0,
      "end_time": 243606.0,
      "text": "and you need people that need something to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243630.0,
      "end_time": 244840.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a better way."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 244864.0,
      "end_time": 247167.0,
      "text": "And the good news is, it&#39;s not that complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 247680.0,
      "end_time": 250136.0,
      "text": "This a 2006 Dodge van."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 250494.0,
      "end_time": 253146.0,
      "text": "It was in my motor pool not doing anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 253170.0,
      "end_time": 256111.0,
      "text": "We put some new tires on it, wrapped it with a logo."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 256136.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259931.00000000003,
      "text": "This van now goes out to street corners where our panhandlers are --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 259954.0,
      "end_time": 261144.0,
      "text": "we go to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 261676.0,
      "end_time": 263122.0,
      "text": "We stop the van, we get out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 263146.0,
      "end_time": 265178.0,
      "text": "we ask them if they would like a day&#39;s work"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 265202.0,
      "end_time": 267161.0,
      "text": "rather than panhandling for the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 268161.0,
      "end_time": 270520.0,
      "text": "And if you wondered if they really mean it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 271755.0,
      "end_time": 274712.0,
      "text": "it takes us about an hour to fill this van up in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 274736.0,
      "end_time": 278155.0,
      "text": "because almost everybody we ask takes a job for the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279193.0,
      "end_time": 280854.0,
      "text": "But you need more than just a van."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 281407.0,
      "end_time": 284330.0,
      "text": "You need a super-fantastic human being to drive that van."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 285960.0,
      "end_time": 287766.0,
      "text": "And my super-fantastic human being, his name is Will."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 287790.0,
      "end_time": 289561.0,
      "text": "This is him in the yellow vest."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 289585.0,
      "end_time": 292119.0,
      "text": "Will works at our local nonprofit partner."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 292143.0,
      "end_time": 293965.0,
      "text": "He works with the homeless every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 293990.0,
      "end_time": 295719.0,
      "text": "The panhandlers trust him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 296516.0,
      "end_time": 297892.0,
      "text": "he believes in them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 298523.0,
      "end_time": 299738.0,
      "text": "he hustles."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 300105.0,
      "end_time": 302738.0,
      "text": "I like to say, \"Where there&#39;s a Will, there&#39;s a way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 303146.0,
      "end_time": 306140.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re going to do the Better Way campaign in your city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306164.0,
      "end_time": 307816.0,
      "text": "you need to find yourself a Will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 309160.0,
      "end_time": 312817.0,
      "text": "because he&#39;s really one of the keys to making this successful"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312841.0,
      "end_time": 314441.0,
      "text": "in the city of Albuquerque."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 314465.0,
      "end_time": 316652.0,
      "text": "You also need a great nonprofit partner."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 316676.0,
      "end_time": 319199.0,
      "text": "Ours is St. Martin&#39;s Hospitality Center."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 319223.0,
      "end_time": 321732.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been in our community for over 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 321756.0,
      "end_time": 324268.0,
      "text": "They provide counseling, food, shelter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 324293.0,
      "end_time": 325696.0,
      "text": "and if they don&#39;t provide it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 325720.0,
      "end_time": 327736.0,
      "text": "they know somebody in our city that does."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 328370.0,
      "end_time": 330813.0,
      "text": "But they do something much more for me as the mayor."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 330837.0,
      "end_time": 332472.0,
      "text": "They provide agility."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 332496.0,
      "end_time": 334709.0,
      "text": "You see, it takes me two weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 334733.0,
      "end_time": 336503.0,
      "text": "maybe two months sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 336527.0,
      "end_time": 339620.0,
      "text": "to onboard an employee with the city of Albuquerque."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 339844.0,
      "end_time": 341599.0,
      "text": "So you could imagine --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 341623.0,
      "end_time": 342792.0,
      "text": "my old Dodge van,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 342816.0,
      "end_time": 345126.0,
      "text": "my super-fantastic human being, Will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 345150.0,
      "end_time": 347440.0,
      "text": "a great local nonprofit partner --"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 347690.0,
      "end_time": 349303.0,
      "text": "they drive to the corner, there&#39;s a panhandler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 349327.0,
      "end_time": 351581.0,
      "text": "they say, \"Would you like to work for the day?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 351605.0,
      "end_time": 352901.0,
      "text": "The panhandler says, \"Yes,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 352925.0,
      "end_time": 356730.0,
      "text": "and Will says, \"Great! I&#39;ll be back in six weeks to pick you up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 356970.0,
      "end_time": 357120.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 357144.0,
      "end_time": 358295.0,
      "text": "It wouldn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 358319.0,
      "end_time": 362558.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really important that we have that agility in our program."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 362582.0,
      "end_time": 364256.0,
      "text": "And they do the paperwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 364280.0,
      "end_time": 365804.0,
      "text": "they do the insurance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 365828.0,
      "end_time": 369149.0,
      "text": "they do all of the other forms that I can&#39;t do quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 369610.0,
      "end_time": 371769.0,
      "text": "We pay our panhandlers nine dollars an hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 372165.0,
      "end_time": 374460.0,
      "text": "We feed them once at the jobsite."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 374700.0,
      "end_time": 375223.0,
      "text": "At the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 375247.0,
      "end_time": 377899.0,
      "text": "our old Dodge van takes them right back to St. Martin&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 377923.0,
      "end_time": 380267.0,
      "text": "and they get connected with counseling services."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 381603.0,
      "end_time": 382785.0,
      "text": "So far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 382809.0,
      "end_time": 385291.0,
      "text": "with the pilot program and a couple days a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 385315.0,
      "end_time": 387978.0,
      "text": "and a fantastic human being and a Dodge van,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 388200.0,
      "end_time": 391398.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve cleaned up 400 city blocks in the city of Albuquerque."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 391422.0,
      "end_time": 395905.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve picked up over 117,000 pounds of trash, weeds and litter."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 395929.0,
      "end_time": 398251.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if you&#39;ve ever weighed a tumbleweed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 398276.0,
      "end_time": 399557.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t weigh much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 399581.0,
      "end_time": 403385.0,
      "text": "so you can imagine the volume of material that we&#39;ve picked up."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 403409.0,
      "end_time": 406358.0,
      "text": "My city has 6,000 employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 407161.0,
      "end_time": 409627.0,
      "text": "and none better than my solid waste department."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 410209.0,
      "end_time": 412357.0,
      "text": "We send our trucks out at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 412381.0,
      "end_time": 414613.0,
      "text": "they help the panhandlers put into the truck"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 414637.0,
      "end_time": 416880.0,
      "text": "the material they&#39;ve picked up during the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 416904.0,
      "end_time": 418407.0,
      "text": "and we take it to the landfill."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 418431.0,
      "end_time": 420195.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m lucky that I have city employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 420219.0,
      "end_time": 423159.0,
      "text": "that are willing to work side by side with our panhandlers."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 423184.0,
      "end_time": 426170.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re lifting up our city while lifting up their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 426194.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "And like anything else -- listen, it takes resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 429284.0,
      "end_time": 432120.0,
      "text": "But the good news is it doesn&#39;t take much."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 433100.0,
      "end_time": 434840.0,
      "text": "We started with an old van,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 434864.0,
      "end_time": 436602.0,
      "text": "a super-fantastic human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 436626.0,
      "end_time": 437919.0,
      "text": "a great local nonprofit"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 437944.0,
      "end_time": 439540.0,
      "text": "and $50,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 440468.0,
      "end_time": 442634.0,
      "text": "But we also had to have community trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 442658.0,
      "end_time": 446205.0,
      "text": "And fortunately, we had built that up in years prior to Better Way."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 446778.0,
      "end_time": 449288.0,
      "text": "We have a program called \"Albuquerque Heading Home,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 449312.0,
      "end_time": 452356.0,
      "text": "a Housing First model where we house the chronically homeless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 452380.0,
      "end_time": 455465.0,
      "text": "and when I told my community we wanted to do that differently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 455489.0,
      "end_time": 458145.0,
      "text": "I said there&#39;s a smart way to do the right thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 458616.0,
      "end_time": 462705.0,
      "text": "We have now housed 650 chronically homeless, medically vulnerable --"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 462729.0,
      "end_time": 465534.0,
      "text": "frankly, most likely to die on the streets in our city."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 466177.0,
      "end_time": 468546.0,
      "text": "We commissioned our university, they studied it."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 468570.0,
      "end_time": 472224.0,
      "text": "We could tell the taxpayers, we can save you 31.6 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 472248.0,
      "end_time": 475823.0,
      "text": "over the cost of leaving someone to struggle for survival on the streets."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 476250.0,
      "end_time": 480248.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve now saved over five million dollars while housing 650 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 480272.0,
      "end_time": 482239.0,
      "text": "So we had that community trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 482263.0,
      "end_time": 485477.0,
      "text": "but we had to have a little bit more of an honest conversation also"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 485502.0,
      "end_time": 486989.0,
      "text": "as a community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 487130.0,
      "end_time": 489390.0,
      "text": "because we had to get people to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 489630.0,
      "end_time": 491606.0,
      "text": "that when they hand those five dollars out the window,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 491630.0,
      "end_time": 494260.0,
      "text": "they might actually be minimizing their opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 494500.0,
      "end_time": 496106.0,
      "text": "to help the person in need, and here&#39;s why:"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 496130.0,
      "end_time": 499943.0,
      "text": "that five dollars might go to buying some fast food today --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 499967.0,
      "end_time": 502469.0,
      "text": "a lot of times it goes to buying drugs and alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 502992.0,
      "end_time": 504143.0,
      "text": "That same five dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 504167.0,
      "end_time": 506424.0,
      "text": "if you gave it to one of our shelters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 506449.0,
      "end_time": 508210.0,
      "text": "could feed seven people today."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 508234.0,
      "end_time": 512515.0,
      "text": "And if you gave it to one of our local food banks or food pantries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 512539.0,
      "end_time": 515490.0,
      "text": "we could actually feed 20 people with that money."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 517711.0,
      "end_time": 522558.0,
      "text": "People ask,\"Well, Albuquerque is 600,000 people -- million, metro --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 522582.0,
      "end_time": 525674.0,
      "text": "this wouldn&#39;t work in our city, we&#39;re too big, we&#39;re too small.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 525698.0,
      "end_time": 528393.0,
      "text": "I disagree; if you have one panhandler on one city block,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 528417.0,
      "end_time": 529573.0,
      "text": "you can do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 529597.0,
      "end_time": 532215.0,
      "text": "If you live in a city of eight-and-half million people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 532239.0,
      "end_time": 533394.0,
      "text": "you can do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 533418.0,
      "end_time": 534895.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t matter what you do."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 534919.0,
      "end_time": 537781.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not the work that you do, it&#39;s the dignity of the work."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 537805.0,
      "end_time": 538963.0,
      "text": "You could do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 538987.0,
      "end_time": 541870.0,
      "text": "So I think any city could do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 541111.0,
      "end_time": 542310.0,
      "text": "And people say to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 542334.0,
      "end_time": 544397.0,
      "text": "\"Mayor, that&#39;s just a little too simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 545197.0,
      "end_time": 547281.0,
      "text": "It can&#39;t work that way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 547305.0,
      "end_time": 548853.0,
      "text": "But I tell you what, friends:"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 548878.0,
      "end_time": 550321.0,
      "text": "when you go to a street corner"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 550345.0,
      "end_time": 553273.0,
      "text": "and you engage with a panhandler with dignity and respect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 553297.0,
      "end_time": 555997.0,
      "text": "maybe for the first time in years, maybe in their life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 556210.0,
      "end_time": 558750.0,
      "text": "and you tell them that you believe in them"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 558100.0,
      "end_time": 560772.0,
      "text": "and that this is their city as much as it&#39;s your city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 560796.0,
      "end_time": 565563.0,
      "text": "and that you actually need their help to make our place better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 565587.0,
      "end_time": 568905.0,
      "text": "and you understand that this isn&#39;t the answer to all their problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 568929.0,
      "end_time": 570847.0,
      "text": "but at least it&#39;s a start,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 570871.0,
      "end_time": 572513.0,
      "text": "an amazing thing happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 573730.0,
      "end_time": 576419.0,
      "text": "When they get out on the jobsite and they start working together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 576443.0,
      "end_time": 578340.0,
      "text": "you start seeing amazing things happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 578364.0,
      "end_time": 581667.0,
      "text": "They see teamwork; they see the fact that they can make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 581691.0,
      "end_time": 582932.0,
      "text": "And at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 582956.0,
      "end_time": 585652.0,
      "text": "when they get back to St. Martin&#39;s in that old Dodge van,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 585676.0,
      "end_time": 589400.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re much more likely to sign up for whatever services they need --"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 589280.0,
      "end_time": 591747.0,
      "text": "substance abuse, mental health counseling, you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 591771.0,
      "end_time": 594190.0,
      "text": "So far with our pilot program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 594215.0,
      "end_time": 597840.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve offered about 1,700 days of day work."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 597108.0,
      "end_time": 601223.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve connected 216 people to permanent employment opportunities."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 601687.0,
      "end_time": 605358.0,
      "text": "Twenty people actually qualified for our Housing First model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 605382.0,
      "end_time": 606560.0,
      "text": "Heading Home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 606584.0,
      "end_time": 607742.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve been housed."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 607767.0,
      "end_time": 609926.0,
      "text": "And over 150 people have been connected"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 609950.0,
      "end_time": 612768.0,
      "text": "to mental health substance abuse services"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 612792.0,
      "end_time": 614488.0,
      "text": "through There&#39;s a Better Way."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 614512.0,
      "end_time": 617148.0,
      "text": "This is me just two weeks ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 618758.0,
      "end_time": 619926.0,
      "text": "at St. Martin&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 619950.0,
      "end_time": 621402.0,
      "text": "doing our point-in-time survey"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 621426.0,
      "end_time": 622803.0,
      "text": "that we do every two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 623369.0,
      "end_time": 626782.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m interviewing a gentleman who&#39;s homeless, like we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 626806.0,
      "end_time": 629550.0,
      "text": "getting his information, figuring out where he&#39;s from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 629574.0,
      "end_time": 631301.0,
      "text": "how he got there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 631326.0,
      "end_time": 632929.0,
      "text": "what we can do to help him."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 632953.0,
      "end_time": 636924.0,
      "text": "And you notice he&#39;s holding the same sign that the guy was holding in 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 636948.0,
      "end_time": 639500.0,
      "text": "same sign I walked out with here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 639987.0,
      "end_time": 642959.0,
      "text": "So you have to ask yourself: Is it really making a difference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 642983.0,
      "end_time": 644992.0,
      "text": "Absolutely it&#39;s making a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 645160.0,
      "end_time": 647674.0,
      "text": "Albuquerque is now one of the national leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 647698.0,
      "end_time": 650924.0,
      "text": "in combating some of the most stubborn and persistent social issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 650948.0,
      "end_time": 652980.0,
      "text": "that we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 652123.0,
      "end_time": 654200.0,
      "text": "Combined with Albuquerque Heading Home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 654260.0,
      "end_time": 655217.0,
      "text": "the Better Way program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 655241.0,
      "end_time": 658181.0,
      "text": "Albuquerque has reduced unsheltered homelessness in our city"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 658205.0,
      "end_time": 660191.0,
      "text": "by 80 percent last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 661223.0,
      "end_time": 662536.0,
      "text": "Since I took over as mayor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 662561.0,
      "end_time": 665825.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve been able to reduce the chronic homeless population in our city"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 665849.0,
      "end_time": 667780.0,
      "text": "by 40 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 667950.0,
      "end_time": 669265.0,
      "text": "And by HUD&#39;s definition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 669289.0,
      "end_time": 670982.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve gotten to functional zero,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 671600.0,
      "end_time": 673654.0,
      "text": "which means we&#39;ve literally ended veteran homelessness"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 673678.0,
      "end_time": 675180.0,
      "text": "in the city of Albuquerque,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 675420.0,
      "end_time": 676472.0,
      "text": "by being intentional."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 676496.0,
      "end_time": 679802.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 682777.0,
      "end_time": 685988.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m happy to report that other cities are hearing about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 686120.0,
      "end_time": 687555.0,
      "text": "other mayors are calling us --"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 687580.0,
      "end_time": 690303.0,
      "text": "Chicago, Seattle, Denver, Dallas --"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 690327.0,
      "end_time": 692863.0,
      "text": "and are now starting to implement programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 692887.0,
      "end_time": 695962.0,
      "text": "where they bring the dignity of work to the equation."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 695986.0,
      "end_time": 697841.0,
      "text": "And I can&#39;t wait to learn from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 697865.0,
      "end_time": 700542.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t wait to see what their experiment looks like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 700566.0,
      "end_time": 702601.0,
      "text": "what their pilot project looks like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 702625.0,
      "end_time": 705198.0,
      "text": "so we can start taking a collective approach nationally"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 705222.0,
      "end_time": 706598.0,
      "text": "through the dignity of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 706622.0,
      "end_time": 708200.0,
      "text": "And I want to commend them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 708270.0,
      "end_time": 710438.0,
      "text": "the mayors, their communities, their nonprofits --"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 710462.0,
      "end_time": 712620.0,
      "text": "for the work that they&#39;re doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 712674.0,
      "end_time": 713973.0,
      "text": "So who&#39;s next?"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 715313.0,
      "end_time": 717764.0,
      "text": "Are you and your city ready to step up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 718590.0,
      "end_time": 722277.0,
      "text": "Are you ready to think differently about these persistent social issues?"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 722780.0,
      "end_time": 725960.0,
      "text": "Are you ready to lift people up in your community"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 725120.0,
      "end_time": 727490.0,
      "text": "through the dignity of work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 727730.0,
      "end_time": 730420.0,
      "text": "and make your city profoundly better in many ways?"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 731310.0,
      "end_time": 734329.0,
      "text": "Well, if you are, my friends, I promise you there is a better way."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 734353.0,
      "end_time": 735511.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 735535.0,
      "end_time": 738939.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}